  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    International Centre for Settlement of Investment Disputes (ICSID) panels: UK appointments announced
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">Department for International Trade (DIT) announces new appointments to the ICSID panel of arbitrators and panel of conciliators.</p>

  </div>
</div>

